            <p>
                Our Purpose at College of Purity Pvt. Ltd. Is to revolutionize the procurement process of schools and
                colleges and similar institutions in India through our E-commerce portal. <br><br>

                Educational Institutions still rely on local market for their needs and procure material through vendors
                known to them or available in nearby market. We want to become a one stop shop solution provider for
                educational institution across India and remove the lacunae this sector faces in procurement.<br><br>

                With experience of over 50 years in the field and hands-on experience of dealing with the requirement of
                schools and colleges day in day out one of the Directors at College of Purity Pvt Ltd : Ankit Kabra had
                a vision to scale-up the existing setup of stock and sell to an online e-commerce entity that serves
                schools and colleges and other institutions pan-india and strives to remove the bottle necks that
                exists-in the procurement process of schools and colleges. Being in the industry Ankit realized that his
                customers faced difficulty in sourcing products that range from cleaning solutions to sanitation to lab
                solutions to hardware, gardening, stationary and so on and so forth and had a vision to provide a one
                stop solution to his customers to bring about a change in this sector in line with todays digital world
                that is all about streamlining with the help of technology.<br><br>

                In order to achieve that Ankit Kabra partnered with Akash Jalan, director at Eyelex films Private Ltd
                and Trustee at Bridgeford group of Schools, Jharkhand and experience of several other businesses to form
                College Of Purity Pvt. Ltd. that has a vision of serving Schools and Colleges across the length and
                breadth of the country.
            </p>

