            </p>

            <h2 class="page-heading" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">Genesis</h2>
            <p>
                112, its inspiration comes from the ancient Indian vedic scripture called Vijñāna Bhairava Tantra which
                is a discourse between Bhairava (Lord Shiva) and Bhairavi (Goddess Parwati) and briefly presents 112
                techniques of meditation for self-reanimation. It’s a gift for mankind to understand life and self
                actualize through service.
                <br><br>

                112cart.com strives to find inspiration from the same goal of spirituality and believes that everything
                in this world from business to service should be done with this purity. Purity in business and service
                is our motto. Service is Salvation is our tagline.
                <br><br>

                College of Purity Private Limited is also working on bringing these 112 tantrik meditations or methods
                of meditation to everyone in the world through its digital avatar called 112ways.com.
                <br><br>

                We strive to propagate message of purity through various means in the modern world. E-commerce, Apps,
                Motion Pictures, Books and whatever the universe presents are our means to propagate our understanding
                of PURITY.
                <br><br>

                Purity for us is action that’s in conformity with the universe and aligned with its ethos. Purity is
                acting with a sense of service to the customer and community at large. Purity is every moment behavior
                that takes into account the well being of all parties involved. Purity is to be a part of something that
                contributes and get the benefits as a byproduct. Purity is to work without the stimuli of greed and
                fear.
